      "content": "i feel like i’ve hit a wall and i don't think i can climb it again. everything i worked for in this program... the funding fell through, the last six months of lab work were basically for nothing. i'm just so tired. not even the kind of tired sleep fixes. just... finished. like i've run out of things to give.",
